{"tid":482991,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"新手玩dap","createTime":"2017-11-28T16:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T11:38:27.000Z","uid":41824,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a2aa2423c6b801f85d6e903154d4b673b2961c3c","tid":482991,"uid":41824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T16:43:05.000Z","msg":"3000內有咩dap介紹，如果行android 個啲點睇？<br />\n另外想問下各位係咩地方搵歌，付費個啲都得，moov個啲點睇？<br />\n小弟係新手一名，求指教"},{"pid":"8a5a928dc8e2abcb1c4aa558c5516e09363bb286","tid":482991,"uid":54999,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T16:45:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3feb46d8c284cf58119109ab1998ad239a94249f","tid":482991,"uid":41824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T16:57:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1500夠啦，投資耳筒好過</blockquote><br />\n有咩好介紹？"},{"pid":"e8697bfdb0c8458006082600406101cf5c69b977","tid":482991,"uid":54999,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T17:10:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b43d5e4f38abd6a53007bfa2a08b3170445898e8","tid":482991,"uid":22318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T04:51:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1500夠啦，投資耳筒好過</blockquote><br />\n有咩好介紹？</blockquote><br />\n30r?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c2239071cc91e2067949516af7993c84f84af1","tid":482991,"uid":35889,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T04:56:04.000Z","msg":"樓上真係鳩噏到呢...<br />\n<br />\n你耳機用緊咩?<br />\n<br />\n無耳機既話,耳機+DAP預算幾多?<br />\n<br />\n聽開D咩?"},{"pid":"006bf509a5aa4362e1504750fa95225da15e5593","tid":482991,"uid":41824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:13:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上真係鳩噏到呢...<br />\n<br />\n你耳機用緊咩?<br />\n<br />\n無耳機既話,耳機+DAP預算幾多?<br />\n<br />\n聽開D咩?</blockquote><br />\n4000內可以？<br />\n好雜食，咩都聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe5702f871e7a247e026367326b2983e54f128e","tid":482991,"uid":33429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T22:43:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓上真係鳩噏到呢...<br />\n<br />\n你耳機用緊咩?<br />\n<br />\n無耳機既話,耳機+DAP預算幾多?<br />\n<br />\n聽開D咩?</blockquote><br />\n4000內可以？<br />\n好雜食，咩都聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會揀all in 耳機<br />\n第時有閒錢屎忽痕再買dap"},{"pid":"6f5ed07a6076da7d2bcba115221d4757775d3ec9","tid":482991,"uid":123296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T00:02:46.000Z","msg":"3000-4000買部dap都差唔多用哂畢直<br />\n有dap用廢耳機又怪怪地，<br />\n不如all in耳機先<br />\n遲啲有錢再買dap"},{"pid":"dfdbe4dac16951dbd985295cd275cae0e7a4aaf7","tid":482991,"uid":103902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T00:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d82d298ad03b044f29651a919c2e39da5fcee6e","tid":482991,"uid":11088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T00:50:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係靚嘅耳機係唔會預你用來講電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be1d935bee95463eb499c5b4de264aa9a339561","tid":482991,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T01:03:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無試聽過先？耳機呢d野一定要親身試聽睇下睇下啱唔啱口味，買過次罩奶左野，幾日就放番出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9b1244a152d7bf6dcb4c7b192924970a551f31","tid":482991,"uid":36284,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T01:03:36.000Z","msg":"4000樓下大把耳機款可以揀 你就算用電話輸出都明顯聽到有分別<br />\n唔自己行出街試唔會知邊隻岩你<br />\n<br />\n例如鍾意人聲前d可以試 se425 想要多番小小bass 又可以試下 535 <br />\n想玩下圈鐵混合又可以試下 fender<br />\n唔試過淨睇文字唔會搵到岩自己既野"},{"pid":"77089075964c407e063bea63f81795d75b4a9ca4","tid":482991,"uid":123296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T02:14:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4000樓下大把耳機款可以揀 你就算用電話輸出都明顯聽到有分別<br />\n唔自己行出街試唔會知邊隻岩你<br />\n<br />\n例如鍾意人聲前d可以試 se425 想要多番小小bass 又可以試下 535 <br />\n想玩下圈鐵混合又可以試下 fender<br />\n唔試過淨睇文字唔會搵到岩自己既野</blockquote><br />\n都仲有qdc 3單元<br />\nue 4pro 等等大牌子簡<br />\n唔一定要shure<br />\n不過都係要自己去試<br />\n口味個個唔同，無話邊隻一定啱<br />\n反正試又唔做俾錢，<br />\n係要少少時間姐"},{"pid":"ff98238525eafd1caa06d397ebc09e43b2a41738","tid":482991,"uid":6594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T02:35:33.000Z","msg":"要玩串流既話日水300R啦"},{"pid":"99709a5dc152beae8f5cb5e72e29edd465f0f6d5","tid":482991,"uid":18283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T02:42:37.000Z","msg":"shure = 垃圾"},{"pid":"b5af23a72814b92f01f96b073ab48539d3784d05","tid":482991,"uid":41824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T06:44:20.000Z","msg":"如果2000到，有咩耳機介紹？"},{"pid":"65c1e39f5e2315b8822be6ed3f00c4c977835b10","tid":482991,"uid":123296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:50:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果2000到，有咩耳機介紹？</blockquote><br />\nqdc 海王星<br />\n鐵三角 ls200 人聲靚小小 base無咁勁"},{"pid":"fd4bfac12622351ff431ba148854334c13daf740","tid":482991,"uid":157453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:05:39.000Z","msg":"搭單問，用緊iPod touch + ath ck100pro <br />\n可以點入dap 坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6439b6fb478c1a85800d2f8faeffa3379a2252d4","tid":482991,"uid":10233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T10:02:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4000樓下大把耳機款可以揀 你就算用電話輸出都明顯聽到有分別<br />\n唔自己行出街試唔會知邊隻岩你<br />\n<br />\n例如鍾意人聲前d可以試 se425 想要多番小小bass 又可以試下 535 <br />\n想玩下圈鐵混合又可以試下 fender<br />\n唔試過淨睇文字唔會搵到岩自己既野</blockquote><br />\n唔好出嚟害人啦好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12cfe376be9f7d9445dbf275a1750ef420179f7d","tid":482991,"uid":41824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T10:16:37.000Z","msg":"唔該曬各位巴打，下星期去試上面個幾款，請問邊到多耳機試？"},{"pid":"e56bb084e9bb4cd69a90208756b51d8692c396ab","tid":482991,"uid":123296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T10:21:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問，用緊iPod touch + ath ck100pro <br />\n可以點入dap 坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去試下dap囉<br />\n同一對耳機都會有唔同感覺嘅聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0112f2dda7f481b0f39ce422e436577f64e44f2","tid":482991,"uid":123296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T10:23:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔該曬各位巴打，下星期去試上面個幾款，請問邊到多耳機試？</blockquote><br />\n亦軒耳機音樂世界<br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多好多好多耳機免費任試，面皮夠厚既話，可試足一個下午<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貨品種類繁多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分店多，地點便利<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 亦軒論壇個二手買賣區，間中會搵到筍野(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你一定要知價，否則做水魚)<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貨品價錢偏貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，大部份貨品都賣貴過甚他鋪頭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開左鋪後，佢個論壇變了質，好多野都俾人大吹一餐，或人云亦云，D意見睇下就算，最緊要親自試聽<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人流多，唔少耳機都俾人試到殘晒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n金聲耳筒專門店<br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔少耳機都可以任試 (但冇亦軒咁多)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總店人流較少，環境靜D，可以專心D試耳機，耳機也比較新淨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分店多，地點尚算方便<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢比亦軒平<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買野前切記一定要問清楚是行定水貨、保養條款、檢查行貨包裝上有沒有香港代理的貼紙和標籤<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAV2000<br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢[rgb(255, 192, 203)]通常比其他鋪頭[/rgb(255, 192, 203)]平，會講明係行貨定水貨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 據聞個老闆以前在某影音鋪打工，對影音產品既意見較專業<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜撚野都冇得試<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鋪頭細小，貨品款式不及亦軒、金聲咁多，更沒有售賣大陸牌子耳機，以大牌子的熱門貨品為主<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDMA 泛音<br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多高檔野試<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有D牌子都做返街價<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有出自己牌子既HP架，都有ATH架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有SOUND CARD，DAC，AMP，喇叭，DAP賣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牌子相對比較齊<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 某D牌子仍屬於貴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢賣既多數都係高檔貨，小朋友玩唔起，得個睇字 (依家其實都有唔少入門野賣)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇DENON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nJaben HK<br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多貴野試，做cm可以即場做埋耳印<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁多間入面試耳機最好環境，閒日時間少人夠晒靜，任試唔嬲<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比較貴，視姦play<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恆源<br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有自家品牌，地方比較靜<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D產品都係戇鳩調音，乜都賣得貴過人，馬撚又小器又封閉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天下影音：(16/F) <br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有D貨會劈價<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係比較有名氣牌子 (唔會有大陸牌子)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 賣HI-FI種類多，有興趣巴打可以順便望望<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行內消息：由Denon代理開既 (好難証實，但有Denon野賣，DMA係冇Denon野)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有分店，但System及貨量都係獨立，所以佢既分店呢間冇可以走去第間睇睇或者格價<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試既多數係HP<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有平野賣，但唔多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要格價(拿，唔好話我唔提)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 限定版唔洗諗，應該好難會入到手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行內消息：T字頭代理會唔派貨，正如AX2XXX咁 (原因都係個價做壞市)，換句話講唔一定有HIT既貨品<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似冇MONSTER貨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華仁：(10/F)<br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢都肯追貼街價<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 環境好 (但唔太靜，如果有人試HI-FI)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有HI-FI野睇同小量DAC/AMP野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有BD賣 (價錢唔好諗佢平)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 店員幾NICE (第一次上去果時，第二次就差D笑容，但佢都樂意拎俾你聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 旗艦級IEM都有得試，etc. IE8、SE535<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牌子小 只有ATH SEN記 加MONSTER同SHURE<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢唔好最平<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 主打HI-FI 所以唔好望D野好齊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 容納人數小，試聽頂多4、5人已經叫FULL<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英京：(8/F)<br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同天下(16/F)差唔多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感覺AMP/DAC種類較多(對比16/F)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試耳機服務好過(16/F)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可訂貨<br />\n<br />\nBAD <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同天下(16/F)差唔多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地唔太SURE停產與否，都會叫你訂貨，例如W1000 (某D對呢方面唔太熟既職員會咁做)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國際影音：(7/F)<br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒男O岩，望價睇野，佢都唔點理你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢都同友誠上下撞<br />\n<br />\nBAD <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牌子少<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔太多耳機選擇<br />\n<br />\nRIGHT SHOP<br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多線同耳機有得試<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有QDC (代理啊光開咗第二間舖搬咗去星際三樓fantasy sound)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鋒哥好好人<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人流比以前多左<br />\n<br />\nLet's Go Audio<br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 員工好好人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多嘢有得試，如：耳機、線<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得灣仔有鋪<br />\n<br />\nHOT EARPHONE PRO<br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 員工好Friendly<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有HK Handmade 耳機線賣，好多選擇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有好多鐵三角行貨<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牌子唔算多<br />\n<br />\nMASTER PRO<br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貨品繁多，好多都有得試<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢跟貼街價<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鋪頭比較細<br />\n<br />\nR-Studio<br />\n星際2樓<br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老闆好Friendly<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有整升級線，接口好齊，A2DC都有<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢貼市<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鋪頭細，牌子唔算多<br />\n<br />\nApex Headphone<br />\n星際3樓<br />\n<br />\nGOOD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老闆幾好傾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有耳牛試，有部UD503<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢貼市<br />\n<br />\nBAD<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日都有熟客係度吹水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484dd252f319f6f2d977c46f983abc9bea03439f","tid":482991,"uid":41824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T11:38:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔該